## Authenticate



This API authenticates against partner portal or Commvault core product depending on customer is partner customer or standalone customer respectively. Use the `username` and `password` provided by metallic. Returns `authToken` which is `jwt` token or `QSDK` token based on customer is partner customer or standalone customer respectively.

#### Request Body

| **Field** | **Description** | **Type** | **Required** | **Notes** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| username | Service principal name or user email | String | True |  |
| password | User password | String | True | For standalone customers, `password` must be in base64 encoded format. |

#### Response Body

| **Field** | **Description** | **Type** | **Notes** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| authToken | Authentication token | String | This needs to be passed as `Bearer token` in `Authorization` header for rest of the API calls. |
